  {
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Thanks, <@U5T9JLUAE>, I had contacted both Dave and Glen before I posted here about it, but haven’t heard back yet. But turns out I know enough people who have connections to it, and bumped into even more people I know when I visited yesterday. Fascinating.\n\nI only had an hour, but already had my mind blown several times, so it’ll take me a while — and another visit — to make up my mind and tell you more about it here.\n\nI’d love to share more info on what the rules are around visiting, but I couldn’t yet speak to somebody official enough about it. There were lots of “volunteers” last night. Apparently, they are trying something they call “community hours”, but it doesn’t appear to be official just yet. I will report as soon as I learn more.",
